title: The 8th Annual Producer's Perspective Social
desc: Davenport Theatrical Enterprises invites you to... The 8th Annual Producer's Perspective Social ? Thursday, December 17th 7pm - 9pm Hurley's Saloon 232 W 48th St, First Floor (Between Broadway and 8th) Come celebrate the end of the year with Davenport Theatrical and meet writers, producers, actors, and other folks just like you. (NOTE: Your RSVP only guarantees your admission. If you would like to bring a guest, please have them RSVP separately.)
